---
description: Enforce SCSS best practices, kebab naming, and file organization.
globs: src/**/*.scss
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use `cp` prefix for root level or module level selectors, to avoiding collision of styles with consuming apps. Example: `.cp-side-menu`.
- Use `kebab-cased` class names with SCSS nesting
- Never use hard-coded values, use the CSS variables in the "reset.scss"
- **Property Order**: Use a logical property order (Layout -> Box Model -> Typography -> Visual).
